FBIS4-41424 "drsov122_m_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-122 Daily Report 24 Jun 1994 Tajikistan Bus Carrying Children of Russian Soldiers Attacked Bus Carrying Children of Russian Soldiers Attacked LD2406062694 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0620 GMT 24 Jun 94 LD2406062694 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] [Text] Dushanbe June 24 TASS -- One passer-by was killed and another wounded on Friday in Dushanbe when unknown gunmen fired a grenade at a bus carrying children of Russian military servicemen in Tajikistan and their guards. Nobody among the bus passengers was wounded, TASS was told at the Tajik Interior Ministry.
